"Usage: %s [-l <lang>] [-f <format>] [-e <eos>] [--] [<file>]\n"
"Tokenize a file.\n"
"\n"
"Options:\n"
"   -l, --lang=<string>      tokenization language [en]\n"
"   -f, --format=<string>    token format string [%%s\\n]\n"
"   -e, --eos=<string>       string to append at the end of a sentence [\\n]\n"
"   -L, --list               display a list of the available languages\n"
"   -h, --help               display this message\n"
"       --version            display the library version\n"
